_column_text]\n<h3>How do we do it?</h3>\nWe ask the right questions to build a collaborative approach to help your business, after all your needs are different to other schools and your students want something different. Identifying who your customers are, the reasons the make decisions and helping to improve enrolments is how we measure our success. We stay ahead of market trends to help you navigate the uncertainities of going offshore and start really scaling your growth.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Learn more about our services\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"arrow-with-circle\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/services/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About us','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave-v1','','','2015-07-07 08:46:56','2015-07-07 08:46:56','',2,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/2-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(187,2,'2015-07-05 05:03:51','2015-07-05 05:03:51','[vc_row el_class=\"contact-person-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436072535141{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"127\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WHAT EDEX DO?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are a complete end to end solution for education providers - we get students to look at your website, make an enquiry, help your conversions and enrolments and take your business offshore. Regulatory requirements and audits as well as getting you on the register. Our business is to help take your business into new markets and increase your student enrolments. A straight talking, common sense approach to the big issues facing your business and offering the solutions required to grow.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in 