ors to help stakeholders trust you and your brand.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436171712027{background-color: #c7eade !important;}\" el_class=\".image-left-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"119\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Digital Intelligence</h3>\r\nYou\'re a digital immigrant trying to work with digital natives, and just like speaking another language there\'s being able to speak another language with some basic conversational phrases and being able to speak another language. We know where your customers live, where they spend their time and how they like to access information to make their decisions about studying. We do the deep dive on social media channels, customer profiling and write the communications that will resonate with prospective students and get them to make an enquiry and go onto enrol.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436170388734{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\" el_class=\".image-right-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"124\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Customer Management</h3>\r\nIt\'s easy to get people to look at your website and download a brochure, but this is only the first step. Your sales team, marketing team and customer service team all impact on your bottom line - and it is absolutely critical to make sure that your teams are all working together to keep the students after you convert the leads.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"contact-form-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][contact-form-7 id=\"79\" title=\"Contact Us\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 07:13:46','2015-07-07 07:13:46','',12,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(218,2,'2015-07-07 07:14:46','2015-07-07 07:14:46','','Business Development','','inherit','open','open','','edex_image_04','','','2015-07-07 07:14:57','2015-07-07 07:14:57','',12,'http://edex.martintutko.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Edex_Image_04.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(219,2,'2015-07-07 07:15:39','2015-07-07 07:15:39','[vc_row el_class=\".contact-person-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436170141805{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"212\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"small\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Services</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We can take the load off of you, and tailor the best solution for you and your college. We decode the choices to provide simple common sense tactics to grow your business.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436171277775{background-color: #ebebeb !important;}\" el_class=\".image-left-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"216\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Market Research</h3>\r\nYou need intelligent information, curated content that is distilled into a format that is easily digested and helps you make decisions quickly. Our approach to research is to take the work off you, and combine the data and synthesise this into information. Studies, market reports, online analytics, trends, sales, marketing, competitor performance all combined into the 