it','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 07:24:56','2015-07-07 07:24:56','',60,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(227,2,'2015-07-07 07:27:10','2015-07-07 07:27:10','','Contact Icon','','inherit','open','open','','contact_icon','','','2015-07-07 07:27:21','2015-07-07 07:27:21','',29,'http://edex.martintutko.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Contact_Icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(228,2,'2015-07-07 07:27:27','2015-07-07 07:27:27','[vc_row el_class=\"contact-person-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436171145724{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"227\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"small\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1436170950265{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Feel free to email us</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"contact-form-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][contact-form-7 id=\"79\" title=\"Contact Us\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Contact us','','inherit','open','open','','29-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 07:27:27','2015-07-07 07:27:27','',29,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/29-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(229,2,'2015-07-07 08:43:37','2015-07-07 08:43:37','','Digital Intelligence','','inherit','open','open','','digital_intelligence_02','','','2015-07-07 08:43:52','2015-07-07 08:43:52','',12,'http://edex.martintutko.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Digital_Intelligence_02.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(230,2,'2015-07-07 08:43:55','2015-07-07 08:43:55','[vc_row el_class=\".contact-person-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436170141805{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"212\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"small\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Services</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We can take the load off of you, and tailor the best solution for you and your college. We decode the choices to provide simple common sense tactics to grow your business.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436171277775{background-color: #ebebeb !important;}\" el_class=\".image-left-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"216\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Market Research</h3>\r\nYou need intelligent information, curated content that is distilled into a format that is easily digested and helps you make decisions quickly. Our approach to research is to take the work off you, and combine the data and synthesise this into information. Studies, market reports, online analytics, trends, sales, marketing, competitor performance all combined into the right format that help your grow your business and help you make intelligent forecasts.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436170388734{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\" el_class=\".image-right-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"218\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Business Development</h3>\r\nIn education relationships matter, and every relationship requires the right introduction and the great communication. We take the worry out of getting you in front of the right people who will work with you to grow your business. Our extensive network of partners, institutions and agents will be opened to you and we can help you commence building your pipeline. Our reputation can open the doors to help stakeholders trust you and your brand.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436171712027{background-color: #c7eade !important;}\" el_class=\".image-left-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"229\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Digital Intelligence</h3>\r\nYou\'re a digital immigrant trying to work with digital natives, and just like speaking another language there\'s being able to speak another language with some basic conversational phrases and being able to speak another language. We know where your customers live, where they spend their time and how they like to access information to make their decisions about studying. We do the deep dive on social media channels, customer profiling and write the communications that will resonate with prospective students and get them to make an enquiry and go onto enrol.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436170388734{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\" el_class=\".image-right-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"220\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Customer Management</h3>\r\nIt\'s easy to get people to look at your website and download a brochure, but this is only the first step. Your sales team, marketing team and customer service team all impact on your bottom line - and it is absolutely critical to make sure that your teams are all working together to keep the students after you convert the leads.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"contact-form-box\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][contact-form-7 id=\"79\" title=\"Contact Us\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 08:43:55','2015-07-07 08:43:55','',12,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(231,2,'2015-07-07 08:46:27','2015-07-07 08:46:27','','Edex','','inherit','open','open','','businesspeople_v04','','','2015-07-07 08:46:34','2015-07-07 08:46:34','',2,'http://edex.martintutko.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/BusinessPeople_v04.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(232,2,'2015-07-07 08:47:06','2015-07-07 08:47:06','','Edex','','inherit','open','open','','edex_image_06','','','2015-07-07 08:47:16','2015-07-07 08:47:16','',2,'http://edex.martintutko.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Edex_Image_06.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(233,2,'2015-07-07 08:47:42','2015-07-07 08:47:42','[vc_row el_class=\"contact-person-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436072535141{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"225\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"small\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">About Edex</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are a complete end to end solution for education providers - we get students to look at your website, make an enquiry, help your conversions and enrolments and take your business offshore. Regulatory requirements and audits as well as getting you on the register. Our business is to help take your business into new markets and increase your student enrolments. A straight talking, common sense approach to the big issues facing your business and offering the solutions required to grow.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"image-left-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436073168392{background-color: #e6e6e6 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"231\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>What edex do?</h3>\r\nWe are a complete end to end solution for education providers - we get students to look at your website, make an enquiry, help your conversions and enrolments and take your business offshore. Regulatory requirements and audits as well as getting you on the register. Our business is to help take your business into new markets and increase your student enrolments. A straight talking, common sense approach to the big issues facing your business and offering the solutions required to grow.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"contact-person\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/contact-us/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"image-right-box\" css=\".vc_custom_1436074184384{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"232\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>How do we do it?</h3>\r\nWe ask the right questions to build a collaborative approach to help your business, after all your needs are different to other schools and your students want something different. Identifying who your customers are, the reasons the make decisions and helping to improve enrolments is how we measure our success. We stay ahead of market trends to help you navigate the uncertainities of going offshore and start really scaling your growth.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Learn more about our services\" target=\"_self\" color=\"btn-dark-grey\" icon=\"arrow-with-circle\" href=\"http://edex.martintutko.com/services/\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About us','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 08:47:42','2015-07-07 08:47:42','',2,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(234,2,'2015-07-07 08:56:28','2015-07-07 08:56:28','[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1436072251447{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]This following document sets forth the Privacy Policy for the <em>Edex</em> website, <em>www.edex.education</em>.\r\n\r\n<em>Edex</em> is committed to providing you with the best possible customer service experience. <em>Company Name</em> is bound by the Privacy Act 1988 (Crh), which sets out a number of principles concerning the privacy of individuals.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-collection-of-your-personal-information\">Collection of your personal information</h3>\r\nThere are many aspects of the site which can be viewed without providing personal information, however, for access to future <em>Edex</em> customer support features you are required to submit personally identifiable information. This may include but not limited to a unique username and password, or provide sensitive information in the recovery of your lost password.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-sharing-of-your-personal-information\">Sharing of your personal information</h3>\r\nWe may occasionally hire other companies to provide services on our behalf, including but not limited to handling customer support enquiries, processing transactions or customer freight shipping. Those companies will be permitted to obtain only the personal information they need to deliver the service. <em>Edex</em> takes reasonable steps to ensure that these organisations are bound by confidentiality and privacy obligations in relation to the protection of your personal information.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-use-of-your-personal-information\">Use of your personal information</h3>\r\nFor each visitor to reach the site, we expressively collect the following non-personally identifiable information, including but not limited to browser type, version and language, operating system, pages viewed while browsing the Site, page access times and referring website address. This collected information is used solely internally for the purpose of gauging visitor traffic, trends and delivering personalized content to you while you are at this Site.\r\n\r\nFrom time to time, we may use customer information for new, unanticipated uses not previously disclosed in our privacy notice. If our information practices change at some time in the future we will use for these new purposes only, data collected from the time of the policy change forward will adhere to our updated practices.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-changes-to-this-privacy-policy\">Changes to this Privacy Policy</h3>\r\n<em>Company Name</em> reserves the right to make amendments to this Privacy Policy at any time. If you have objections to the Privacy Policy, you should not access or use the Site.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-accessing-your-personal-information\">Accessing Your Personal Information</h3>\r\nYou have a right to access your personal information, subject to exceptions allowed by law. If you would like to do so, please let us know. You may be required to put your request in writing for security reasons. <em>Edex </em>reserves the right to charge a fee for searching for, and providing access to, your information on a per request basis.\r\n<h3 id=\"toc-contacting-us\">Contacting us</h3>\r\n<em>Edex </em>welcomes your comments regarding this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy and would like further information, please contact us by any of the following means during business hours Monday to Friday.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Privacy Policy','','inherit','open','open','','49-revision-v1','','','2015-07-07 08:56:28','2015-07-07 08:56:28','',49,'http://edex.martintutko.com/uncategorized/49-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(235,2,'2015-07-07 08